{"tid":1418492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家怪錯咗香港一芳總代理","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:38:10.000Z","uid":277533,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e89ad8229f9e8ea6bdbf90af96a35ba789d63193","tid":1418492,"uid":277533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:54:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1097897725/posts/10214635842145229?s=1006887339&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1097897725%2Fposts%2F10214635842145229%3Fs%3D1006887339%26sfns%3Dmo&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=66d63f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1097897725/posts/10214635842145229?s=1006887339&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係一位員工嘅心聲<br />\n<br />\n認真，香港總代理個老闆未做一芳既時候係同我做同一行，直接d講係&ldquo;對家&rdquo;，但我都非常尊重佢，佢絕對係一個有承擔有人望嘅商人。希望大家搞清楚先。謝謝！"},{"pid":"f19a86f1d4e6929c64b36293c3ea70a971af37ac","tid":1418492,"uid":277533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:00:21.000Z","msg":"不割席不分化<br />\n不要誤會同路人"},{"pid":"81ab7cd3d9d434e4e7a9e12aa84d20805ed3babd","tid":1418492,"uid":277533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:00:31.000Z","msg":"不割席不分化<br />\n不要誤會同路人"},{"pid":"38fe2bb5d893594e700a3edcf61d699b7c9e43b6","tid":1418492,"uid":277533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:12:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/MaladeGrandViewGarden/photos/a.937228363154522/1071499106394113/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FMaladeGrandViewGarden%2Fphotos%2Fa.937228363154522%2F1071499106394113%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=9573c7e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/MaladeGrandViewGarden/photos/a.937228363154522/1071499106394113/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n我認識一個佢既前員工，就算依家無打佢工，佢都係一樣尊敬佢，俾人去遊行之後放有薪假，唔通係假既咩"},{"pid":"b315f1b496d474417a5a56f3abb00d2ce768